### Definitions: bookings and special bookings\
\
**Traditional booking** \'97 Session scheduled from the calendar; `bookings` row; standard session pricing & ledger.\
\
**Special booking** \'97 A learner\'96expert commercial arrangement that is **not** a traditional calendar session checkout. Deliverable-type special bookings (freelance, prep/review, scoped work with a deadline) use **`freelance_work`** and the lifecycle in \'93Special bookings \'97 lifecycle\'94 below.\
\
**Expert package purchase** \'97 Handled via **`expert_packages`**, **`learner_package_credits`**, **`package_credit_redemptions`**; **not** the same UI lifecycle as deliverable special bookings (no \'93mark complete by deadline\'94 for the package sale itself). See \'93Packages \'97 credits and purchase.\'94\
\
**discount_redemptions** \'97 Discount eligibility tracking only; **not** a special booking.\
\
**booking_offers (optional): on learner accept create `freelance_work` with status \'93offered\'94 and proceed to payment.\cf3 \cb1 \
