\cf2 \cb4 ### Special bookings \'97 lifecycle (deliverable / freelance_work)\
\
- Expert sends a **special booking offer** to the learner with **proposed deadline** (and scope/price per Inbox/offer UI).\
- Learner **accepts** or **declines**.\
  - If **declines:** prompt learner to **message the expert** for a revision; expert may send a **revised offer** (same `freelance_work` row updated or new row with `supersedes_freelance_id` \'97 match schema).\
  - If **accepts:** charge learner **total_charge** using the **non-subscription marketplace fee stack** (taxable base **B** = negotiated offer total before platform/tax; platform 10%; taxes 6% on (B + platform fee)). Write **`transactions`** with `transaction_type` for special/freelance charge and **`freelance_id`** set. **Escrow:** funds held until completion acceptance or timeout below.\
- After **successful payment:** notify expert; show special booking on expert dashboard under upcoming **Bookings** or **Special bookings** as **In progress**, with **deadline**, **Mark as complete**, link to conversation/`booking_id` if applicable.\
- Expert **Mark as complete** (by deadline + grace): optional message and attachments to learner.\
- Learner **accepts** or **declines** completion.\
  - **Accept:** **release payout** to expert (**expert_earnings** = **B** per ledger).\
  - **Decline:** learner must message expert with problem; expert **3 calendar days** to rectify; unresolved \uc0\u8594  **admin_review**.\
- Expert **misses work deadline:** **admin_review**; **3 calendar days grace** after deadline; if still incomplete \uc0\u8594  **refund learner** (full or partial per policy; until policies exist, **admin case-by-case**).\
- Learner **no response** to completion within **3 calendar days** of expert submit \uc0\u8594  **auto-release payout** to expert (same as accept).\
\
### freelance_work \'97 status enum, transitions, keys, payment\
\
**Statuses:** `offered` | `declined` | `accepted_pending_payment` (omit if accept+charge are atomic) | `paid_in_progress` | `completion_submitted` | `completed` | `refunded` | `admin_review`\
\
**Transitions:**\
- `offered` \uc0\u8594  `declined` | \u8594  `accepted_pending_payment` \u8594  `paid_in_progress` (skip middle if payment synchronous).\
- `declined` \uc0\u8594  `offered` (re-offer).\
- `paid_in_progress` \uc0\u8594  `completion_submitted` | \u8594  `admin_review` (missed deadline path).\
- `completion_submitted` \uc0\u8594  `completed` (learner accepts OR 3-day silence) | \u8594  `admin_review` (learner declines) | \u8594  `refunded` (if policy allows).\
- `admin_review` \uc0\u8594  `completed` | `refunded`.\
\
**Foreign keys:** Include **`booking_id`** when tied to an existing traditional booking; else nullable with required **`conversation_id`** and/or originating **`message_id`** per product rules. Every successful charge links **`transactions`** to **`freelance_id`**; store **Stripe PaymentIntent id** on `transactions` or `freelance_work` per schema.\
\
**Payment model:** Charge **total_charge** on learner **accept**; **transfer expert payout (B)** on learner **accept completion** or **3-day silence** after expert marks complete; refunds per deadline/dispute/**Admin \'97 disputes and refunds**.\cf3 \cb1 \
